〈{{lang|en|PPAP}}〉的[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]（{{lang|en|MV}}）於2016年8月25日發布<ref name="national post" />，{{lang|en|MV}}中，Piko太郎身穿一席帶有豹紋蛇紋的黃色服裝，一邊跳著舞，一邊舉起手將不存在的笔、苹果、菠萝組合在一起<ref name="national post" /><ref name="Telegraph" />。歌曲加長版{{lang|en|MV}}於2016年10月27日發布<ref name="national post" />，為宣傳歌曲，Piko太郎另外拍攝一部舞蹈教學影片<ref name="Telegraph">{{Cite web |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/pen-pineapple-apple-pen-wildly-popular-viral-video-will-take-ove/ |title=Pen-Pineapple-Apple-Pen: wildly popular viral video will take over the world whether you like it or not |date=2016-09-27 |first=Adam |last=Boult |work=[[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] |accessdate=2018-02-25 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180225112757/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/pen-pineapple-apple-pen-wildly-popular-viral-video-will-take-ove/ |archivedate=2018-02-25 }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|MV}}最初只在日本學生中廣泛流傳<ref name="setn">{{cite news |title=影／日本最新洗腦神曲「PPAP」　網友：一聽就中毒了！ |url=http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=184703-%E5%BD%B1%EF%BC%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6%E7%A5%9E%E6%9B%B2%E3%80%8CPPAP%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%81%BD%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%81 |accessdate=2016-09-27 |author=三立新闻生活中心 |agency=三立新闻 |date=2016-09-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217135019/https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=184703-%E5%BD%B1%EF%BC%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6%E7%A5%9E%E6%9B%B2%E3%80%8CPPAP%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%81%BD%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%81 |archivedate=2019-02-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rocket">{{Cite web |url=http://rocketnews24.com/2016/09/27/804877/ |script-title=ja:【日本発】動画『ペンパイナッポーアッポーペン』が海外で急速に拡散中！「第2の江南スタイル」「謎の中毒性」と話題 / Tシャツまで販売される事態に |accessdate=2016-09-27 |date=2016-09-27 |work=ロケットニュース24 |language=ja |archivedate=2016-09-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927105042/http://rocketnews24.com/2016/09/27/804877/ |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="蘋果日報">{{cite web |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160924/954649/ |title=【全民惡搞中】日本大叔洗腦神曲　能超越江南大叔的只有你了 |author=謝昇璁 |work=蘋果日報 |date=2016-09-24 |accessdate=2016-09-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928112643/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160924/954649/ |archivedate=2016-09-28 |language=zh |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但到了9月，[[贾斯汀·比伯|贾斯汀·比伯]]在推特上表示「（〈{{lang|en|PPAP}}〉是）我在網路上最喜歡的影片」<ref>{{cite tweet|user=justinbieber |number=780860684426895360 |date=2016-09-28 |title=My favorite video on the internet😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭 |language=en |accessdate=2020-06-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622021013/https://twitter.com/justinbieber/status/780860684426895360 |archivedate=2020-06-22}}</ref><ref name="ORICON NEWS" /><ref name="Shares">{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7525569/justin-bieber-piko-taro-ppap-pen-pineapple-apple-pen-viral-video |title=Justin Bieber Shares His 'Favorite Video on the Internet': Piko Taro's Viral 'PPAP' Clip |date=2016-09-27 |first=Nerisha |last=Penrose |work=Billboard |accessdate=2020-10-20 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020203840/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7525569/justin-bieber-piko-taro-ppap-pen-pineapple-apple-pen-viral-video/ |archivedate=2020-10-20 }}</ref>，至此〈{{lang|en|PPAP}}〉開始廣為流傳，不到一個月，{{lang|en|MV}}就擁有百萬觀看次數<ref name="setn" /><ref name="rocket" /><ref name="Shares" />，在[[9GAG|9GAG]]的[[Facebook|Facebook]]專頁上更超過54萬人按讚<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/9gag/videos/10154978441766840/# |title=9GAG PPAP |accessdate=2016-09-28 |author=9GAG |date=2016-09-25 |publisher=9GAG |website=Facebook |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928101411/https://www.facebook.com/9gag/videos/10154978441766840/ |archivedate=2016-09-28 |language=en |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]評論歌曲之所以可以網路上造成熱潮，是因為「看它不用花腦力」<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37480920 |title=How a 'Pen-Pineapple-Apple-Pen' earworm took over the internet |last=Chen |first=Heather |date=2016-09-27 |newspaper=BBC News |accessdate=2016-09-28 |archivedate=2016-09-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927124008/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37480920 |language=en |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

